<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٥٥٢ - أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6542">‌نَصْرُ بْنُ عَلِيٍّ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1717">‌خَالِدٍ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">‌شُعْبَةُ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5436">‌الْمُحِلِّ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4341">‌عَدِيِّ بْنِ حَاتِمٍ </a>، عَنِ النَّبِيِّ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٧٥⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«اتَّقُوا النَّارَ وَلَوْ بِشِقِّ تَمْرَةٍ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>